node.text:
🍎Teacher Tip🍎 Save all your letters that you send home throughout the year in one place on your computer.

Instead of typing them up every single year, you can just pull up that file and edit! This saved me so much time! 🙌🏽

I put all my letters together in this resource and they’re editable so that you can customize them for your class! Link in my profile if you need a set. http://bit.ly/lettertemplates

node.text:
New Bundle! I’ve been busy creating digital resources over the past year and I wanted to put them all together in one bundle.

These resources would be awesome for a virtual teacher, but they would also be great for in person use!

Lots of these resources would make great no-prep centers and early finisher activities!

Save 30% off all these resources by grabbing this bundle!

Link in profile- https://bit.ly/digitalmegabundle

New Bundle! 🍎 I’ve been asked if I could create a bilingual (English & Spanish) bundle for a while. I was waiting until I had enough resources to create a good bundle and I’m happy to say that it’s here!

This bundle will be added to in the future and the price will increase accordingly.

You can save 30% off all these resources by purchasing this bundle! Link in profile: https://bit.ly/bilingualbundle

node.text: On sale! 🚨 I’ve had requests for 10 drawer cart labels for a long time and I decided to tackle that project this summer. I picked up a couple of carts to work with and I’m in love with how they both turned out! I’m leaving this pre-sale discount on until the set is complete. It should be done tonight or tomorrow morning! Link in profile- https://bit.ly/teachercartlabels
